user_query: Analyze production efficiency trends over time
sql_query:
WITH 
  -- Calculate total usage by bake type and date
  production_volumes AS (
    SELECT /*+ MAX_EXECUTION_TIME(30000) */ 
      EXTRACT(YEAR FROM date) AS year,
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date) AS month,
      bakeType,
      SUM(totalUsage) AS total_usage
    FROM 
      `production_info`
    GROUP BY 
      year, month, bakeType
  ),
  
  -- Calculate waste by type and date
  packaging_waste AS (
    SELECT 
      EXTRACT(YEAR FROM date) AS year,
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date) AS month,
      type,
      SUM(value) AS total_waste
    FROM 
      `pack_waste`
    GROUP BY 
      year, month, type
  ),
  
  -- Calculate hygiene check results by person and date
  hygiene_results AS (
    SELECT 
      EXTRACT(YEAR FROM date) AS year,
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date) AS month,
      personName,
      COUNT(*) AS num_violations
    FROM 
      `person_hyg`
    GROUP BY 
      year, month, personName
  )
  
-- Join the three CTEs to analyze production efficiency trends
SELECT 
  pv.year,
  pv.month,
  pv.bakeType,
  pw.total_waste / pv.total_usage AS waste_ratio,
  hr.num_violations / pv.total_usage AS violation_rate
FROM 
  production_volumes pv
  JOIN packaging_waste pw ON pv.year = pw.year AND pv.month = pw.month AND pv.bakeType = pw.type
  JOIN hygiene_results hr ON pv.year = hr.year AND pv.month = hr.month AND pv.bakeType = hr.personName
ORDER BY 
  year, month, bakeType LIMIT 50

user_query: Analyze price trends for cream over the last 6 months
sql_query:
WITH 
  -- Filter prices table for last 6 months
  recent_prices AS (
    SELECT /*+ MAX_EXECUTION_TIME(30000) */ date, cream FROM prices WHERE date >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 6 MONTH)
  ),
  
  -- Calculate average and max price of cream over time
  avg_max_cream AS (
    SELECT 
      EXTRACT(YEAR FROM date) AS year,
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date) AS month,
      AVG(cream) AS avg_price,
      MAX(cream) AS max_price
    FROM recent_prices
    GROUP BY year, month
  )
  
-- Return average and max price of cream over time
SELECT 
  year,
  month,
  avg_price,
  max_price
FROM avg_max_cream LIMIT 50
